Class DataEncodingType

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.omg.space.xtce.DataEncodingType
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    BinaryDataEncodingType, FloatDataEncodingType, IntegerDataEncodingType, StringDataEncodingType

    public class DataEncodingType
extends java.lang.Object
    Describes how a particular piece of data is sent or received from some non-native, off-platform device. (e.g. a spacecraft)
